title: La Chat in the trap! With Karlous Miller and Clayton English!
itunes:title: La Chat in the trap! With Karlous Miller and Clayton English!
description:
A real Memphis legend is in the trap! "Ms. Chicken Head" La Chat is vibing with Karlous Miller and Clayton English talking bout all that legendary Memphis ish! From Juicy J to Project Pat, La Chat got a dope story and she shares her opinion on what happened in Memphis with Young Dolph. La Chat puts on for the females and shares some of her favorite female MC's. #85southshow
